# API Keys and WiFi Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .tmp/keys.txt and add your actual credentials
#
# Usage: make patch-keys
#
# This file is ignored by git for security
# NEVER commit actual API keys or WiFi passwords to version control

# WiFi Credentials (required for connectivity)
# Format: SET_WIFI=SSID,PASSWORD
# Note: ESP32-S3 only supports 2.4GHz WiFi networks
SET_WIFI=YourNetworkSSID,YourNetworkPassword

# Gemini API Key (optional - required for BTC News feature)
# Get your key at: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_KEY=AIzaSyYourActualGeminiKeyHere

# OpenAI API Key (optional - required for Trading Suggestions feature)
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_KEY=sk-proj-YourActualOpenAIKeyHere

# Notes:
# - Remove any spaces around the = sign
# - Keys should be on a single line
# - WiFi credentials are required; API keys are optional
# - API features won't work without their respective keys
# - You can set credentials individually via serial monitor:
#     SET_WIFI=MyNetwork,MyPassword
#     SET_GEMINI_KEY=AIza...
#     SET_OPENAI_KEY=sk-proj-...
